info.description:
Synthesise data (2D or Healpix) using Cross Scattering Transform (https://arxiv.org/abs/2207.12527) usable for component separation (e.g. denoising). 
 Demo package here : https://github.com/jmdelouis/FOSCAT_DEMO
info.name: foscat
info.summary: Synthesise 2D or Healpix data using Cross Scattering Transform
